high_descs: Turn right and walk around the couch to face the left end of the coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper on the left corner of the coffee table.
Turn around and face the brown chair in front of you.
Put the newspaper down on the brown chair.
Walk around the chair and face the dining room table and face the newspaper.
Pick up the newspaper from the dining room table.
Walk back over to the brown chair with the first newspaper on it.
Place the newspaper down on the brown chair behind the first newspaper.
anns.task_desc: To move two newspapers to the brown chair.

high_descs: Walk right and walk around the couch to the front side, and keep going until you get to the two chairs., then turn around and face the short side of the table.
Pick up the newspaper on the coffee table.
Turn around.
Place the newspaper on the right chair.
Turn right and take a step, then go left to the far side of the table, the long part.
Pick up the newspaper near the gray plate.
Walk back to the chair with the newspaper on it.
Place the newspaper on the chair behind the first newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Place two newspapers on a chair.

high_descs: Go around the couch to stand between the chairs and the coffee table, then turn right and face the coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper that's on the edge of the coffee table.
Turn around with the newspaper and look at the seat of the chair on the right.
Put the newspaper down on the seat of the chair.
Go to the right of the chair and head for the table behind the chairs, then go to the far side of the table and face the corner of it.
Pick up the newspaper on the corner of the table.
Bring the newspaper back to the same chair where the other one is.
Put the newspaper on the seat of the chair so that it forms a T with the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Move the newspapers to the chair.
